<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='398106' id='t-398106'>could be differentiated at different times of day</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='400296' id='t-400296'>depending on how that sun moves across and hits that surface.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 7:00
